<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="sticky-shell">
    <view class="panel">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-header__main">
          <view class="section-title">按站点查询</view>
          <view class="section-subtitle">搜索站点或按线路筛选，查看离你最近的卫生间站点</view>
        </view>
        <view class="section-header__aside">
          <view class="subtle-badge">静态定位演示</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <input class="picker-input" placeholder="搜索站点(在全部站点中搜索)" value="{{searchKeyword}}" bindinput="handleSearchInput" />
      <view wx:if="{{searchKeyword}}" style="margin-top:16rpx;">
        <view class="chip-row" style="justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
          <text class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top:0;">搜索结果</text>
          <text style="color:#667085; font-size:24rpx;" bindtap="handleClearSearch">清空</text>
        </view>
        <block wx:for="{{searchResults}}" wx:key="stationId">
          <view class="picker-item" bindtap="handleOpenStation" data-station-id="{{item.stationId}}" data-line-no="{{item.preferredLineNo}}" data-index="{{index}}">
            <view class="picker-item__content">
              <view class="picker-item__title">{{item.stationName}}</view>
            </view>
            <view class="picker-item__aside">
              <view class="chip-row picker-chip-row">
                <block wx:for="{{item.lineChips}}" wx:key="lineLabel">
                  <view class="line-chip" style="{{item.style}}">{{item.lineLabel}}</view>
                </block>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="info-banner">
      已默认获取你的位置：上海南站附近。当前列表按距离从近到远排序，便于截图展示后续“附近站点推荐”能力。
    </view>
    <view class="panel">
      <view class="section-title" style="font-size:28rpx;">图例</view>
      <view class="legend-grid">
        <block wx:for="{{legends}}" wx:key="key">
          <view class="legend-item">
            <image class="legend-image" src="{{item.iconPath}}" mode="aspectFit" />
            <text>{{item.label}}</text>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="split-layout">
    <scroll-view scroll-y class="browse-sidebar">
      <view class="browse-tab {{activeTab === 'all' ? 'browse-tab--active' : ''}}" bindtap="handleSelectAll">
        全部
      </view>
      <block wx:for="{{browseData.lines}}" wx:key="lineNo">
        <view class="browse-tab {{activeLineNo === item.lineNo ? 'browse-tab--active' : ''}}" style="{{item.lineStyle}}" bindtap="handleSelectLine" data-line-no="{{item.lineNo}}">
          {{item.lineLabel}}
        </view>
      </block>
    </scroll-view>

    <scroll-view scroll-y class="browse-main">
      <block wx:for="{{displayStations}}" wx:key="stationId">
        <view class="list-card" bindtap="handleOpenStation" data-station-id="{{item.stationId}}" data-line-no="{{item.preferredLineNo}}" data-index="{{index}}">
          <view class="list-card__main">
            <view class="list-card__title">{{item.stationName}}</view>
            <view class="list-card__subtitle">距你 {{item.distanceText}}（约{{item.etaText}}）</view>
            <view class="chip-row" style="margin-top:10rpx;">
              <block wx:for="{{item.stationLineChips || item.lineChips}}" wx:key="lineLabel">
                <view class="line-chip" style="{{item.style}}">{{item.lineLabel}}</view>
              </block>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="metric-stack">
            <view class="metric-pill metric-pill--success">{{item.distanceText}}</view>
            <view class="icon-row">
              <block wx:for="{{item.legendIcons}}" wx:key="key">
                <image class="legend-image legend-image--small" src="{{item.iconPath}}" mode="aspectFit" />
              </block>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </block>
      <view wx:if="{{displayStations.length === 0}}" class="empty-state">
        {{emptyText}}
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>
</view>
